#GIIRS preprocessing , SSEC reprocessed L1 data to IODA 
#Wei Han, 08/08/2020

Step1: collect ssec GIIRS  reprocessed files L1 dwell filenames into a file for 1 hour time slot
./prep_file_name.sh yyyymmddhh-begin yyyymmddhh-end
Example: 
./prep_file_name.sh 2020050100 2020050200
Note:
input ssec GIIRS  reprocessed file path
path_input='/ships19/cma/production/FY4A/'

Step2: convert 2 hours GIIRS ssec reprocessed files to ioda netcdf
./giirs2nc_2h.sh yyyymmddhh-begin yyyymmddhh-end 
Example: 
./giirs2nc_2h.sh 2020050100 2020050200

The output giirs ioda files are :
giirs_fy4a_lw_ioda_2020050100.nc4  giirs_fy4a_lw_ioda_2020050112.nc4
giirs_fy4a_lw_ioda_2020050106.nc4  giirs_fy4a_lw_ioda_2020050118.nc4
giirs_fy4a_lw_ioda_2020050200.nc4

Note:
set the output ioda netcdf file path in giirs2nc_2h.sh,
e.g:path_giirs=/data/users/whan/data/obs/giirs_v3/ioda_2h_1